<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-90C9CBD9-2EA5-416E-9AF5-2F7B5C3CCA06" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-90C9CBD9-2EA5-416E-9AF5-2F7B5C3CCA06" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title "> 05 How install the Modification kit of the Aerosol Ink Filter Units (mod 01)</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-0E3E2CA2-5349-4FAF-80F5-347AA9765351"><p class="- topic/p ">This document describes the installation of the modification kit of the Aerosol Ink Filter Units. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Video: 
<xref class="- topic/xref " format="html" href="http://localhost:20346/VIDEO00394EN.US/video07/index.html" scope="external"><?ditaot usertext?>How install the Modification kit of the Aerosol Ink Filter Units</xref> 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_CEA4CD427612471CA3540AD5430B21C2" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_B007BBFF5E5743C89A24651737F64808" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Small screwdriver. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T10 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Cutter 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Magnetizer tool 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-98726AAF-BB3F-4F58-8400-2939AAB281D0" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "/></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-2D7D94A0-B26C-4C0B-B6A3-20C8621663A2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-EEAEFA1A-9258-45B0-B7AF-5EC47CF6C802" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-46479668-0480-496C-80BA-F3344ACA7A13-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-46479668-0480-496C-80BA-F3344ACA7A13-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-BCF9CC76-F25B-4AF8-B39D-9707EF8C6035" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Before you begin</title><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Position manually the Carriage to the left side (chiller side) of the printer. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Place a sheet to protect the platen. 
</p><fig id="GUID-A6A10599-4B7F-41B2-BC6C-B0CA70F23903" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-484B1913-E78A-4ED9-B9B1-C3821013F1E7-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-484B1913-E78A-4ED9-B9B1-C3821013F1E7-low.png"/></fig></li></ol><note id="GUID-09896636-68E1-4A32-A0AD-FD2DC898F45B" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> Use a magnetizer tool to prevent screws from falling down, during the next actions. 
</p></note></section><section id="SECTION_83EFA574E57B4B64A0DD595529E957E2" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Install the modification kit (right-hand side)</title><fig id="GUID-084740A5-EC5B-4001-B705-667D2F45CAAA" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-760693B5-F5FE-42DF-8605-20443201918C-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-760693B5-F5FE-42DF-8605-20443201918C-low.png"/></fig><table id="GUID-BDB87D50-9E70-4086-AC9E-FA7970C76B0D" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the shielding plate. 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Loosen the 4 screws. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove shielding plate. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-43FB0AA9-8131-48D2-9607-058F663E1212" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FC7A44DA-CB3F-4D74-B865-A9AB904CAD9F-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FC7A44DA-CB3F-4D74-B865-A9AB904CAD9F-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the complete mirror box at the right side. 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove clip. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 4 screws that are accessible through the 4 holes. 
</p><note id="GUID-F83C155C-C687-4E87-89B0-88D686FADC78" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> Use the magnetizer tool to prevent screws from falling down. 
</p></note><note id="GUID-0409D4EC-CB28-4E4D-81E4-7168453EB780" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not loosen or remove the red painted screws. 
</p></note></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the mirror box. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-CD526AAA-0A1B-4494-AB12-3BC70F63DB4A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-82EB126A-F154-4B18-A856-E98D67EC0E95-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-82EB126A-F154-4B18-A856-E98D67EC0E95-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-B94F7A7D-CB2F-4CA0-8694-C2A6DBFBD8A0" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-3D463647-FCEC-4E65-AA4B-EF9B906B8AE3-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-3D463647-FCEC-4E65-AA4B-EF9B906B8AE3-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install Bracket on mirror box. 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Mount bracket lock in UPPER position with screw Torx M3x8B. 
</p><note id="GUID-D25A717F-26D4-4713-92FB-3DB4D409986D" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">The screw has to be mount at the left-hand side 
</p></note></li></ul></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-D48AFEC6-1208-4030-A66F-D5BA38EABD27" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0314CF75-EB18-44F5-A4EB-4CE956AC0F39-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0314CF75-EB18-44F5-A4EB-4CE956AC0F39-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the Aerosol Ink Filter Unit. 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Put the T-joint downward in the slit of the hotbox. 
</p><fig id="GUID-27EFC2AD-A2A5-4DAF-8649-C118DBF81D42" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0E3D00E2-CA7B-4C24-8FFA-2D014040FF14-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0E3D00E2-CA7B-4C24-8FFA-2D014040FF14-low.png"/></fig></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-1F3AA524-EE7D-42C9-AF59-E0E61AE3026D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C5919F60-72E0-4094-949E-AB6954CF08AF-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C5919F60-72E0-4094-949E-AB6954CF08AF-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Check</b>: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">After positioning of the Aerosol Ink Filter Unit, the free distance in the slit of the hotbox is nominal 4mm. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-94912C93-B3EF-4E79-A4B6-0EBEDE15B047" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6E845A23-EC84-4839-9C58-1A691228CB9D-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6E845A23-EC84-4839-9C58-1A691228CB9D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the mirror box. 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the 4 screws that are accessible through the 4 holes. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Mount clip. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-C03F02E1-2967-4520-BF18-8629B77414B5" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4188224D-C7F8-4960-8A14-D0B1411023C3-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4188224D-C7F8-4960-8A14-D0B1411023C3-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-15743D1B-3449-4C83-93DB-1CDAA870594C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-7B40E8D8-934D-4AF2-A9F9-D9055221544B-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7B40E8D8-934D-4AF2-A9F9-D9055221544B-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Push bracket lock downwards to secure the Aerosol Ink Filter Unit in vertical direction. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-A329C9FE-8FC7-411A-B870-58C461503B5B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-CAEB71FE-59C5-4FFA-9B35-C04339730958-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CAEB71FE-59C5-4FFA-9B35-C04339730958-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Fix the bracket lock 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Fasten the screw (T M3x8B). 
</p></li></ul></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-88B8943B-2E53-42E3-8A06-4AA57D07E2E8" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-EE7B3017-84D0-42D0-8E84-812A231184F2-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-EE7B3017-84D0-42D0-8E84-812A231184F2-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Connect the harness of the fan. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-350C5601-4896-4626-9BF5-7AC17D515D59" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-449C1283-18EB-46AF-ABC6-C42096C99F01-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-449C1283-18EB-46AF-ABC6-C42096C99F01-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-CAAF4D2B-6778-4D8B-8673-7C67EC8B52B0" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Install the modification kit (left-hand side)</title><fig id="GUID-5E0115E7-D51E-4285-AF19-15EF32A8FD3A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E6F792CF-711D-4AC2-B9E7-6DD2B40631C4-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E6F792CF-711D-4AC2-B9E7-6DD2B40631C4-low.png"/></fig><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-D4DB12A9-67C6-4F89-A7D0-304D4C6F55B4" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the cable ties that fixate the ink tubes to the mirror box. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-4706F67B-C9DF-48A7-952B-7F940B44BBF4" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6004CF9C-C4F9-438E-A8CF-FFBD76B1A2BF-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6004CF9C-C4F9-438E-A8CF-FFBD76B1A2BF-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the clip. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-595D5C00-66EC-4EC5-8F92-00EFC5F09EFE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-737707C5-6FCA-493F-9AF4-1FA97254CA38-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-737707C5-6FCA-493F-9AF4-1FA97254CA38-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the mirror box. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 4 screws that are accessible through the 4 holes and remove the mirror box. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-F21BAAB7-00D1-4834-8EA4-A6E54D44CC76" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove mirror box carefully. 
</p></note><note id="GUID-4BE3439A-63C7-4812-8CA2-F62281E293D8" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> Use the magnetizer tool to prevent screws from falling down. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-20178371-99D0-448A-9F79-2BD24506CC14" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-5797F59C-C5D4-4A14-8829-393D9FE43A56-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-5797F59C-C5D4-4A14-8829-393D9FE43A56-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install Bracket on mirror box. 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Mount bracket lock in UPPER position with screw Torx M3x8B. 
</p><note id="GUID-C053630F-2DBB-4508-927D-560B36E5D20C" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">The screw has to be mount at the right-hand side 
</p></note></li></ul></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-8B6D387C-BF42-48C0-B102-21C4FF501FC1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-93CE161F-27C7-467C-A5D5-F56A3F737E1E-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-93CE161F-27C7-467C-A5D5-F56A3F737E1E-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the Aerosol Ink Filter Unit. 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Put the T-joint downward in the slit of the hotbox. 
</p><fig id="GUID-46B9D7EC-8981-415D-A07A-1D6DCCE7A982" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1880557F-DB1C-46A0-BA1A-C7740940C7A0-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1880557F-DB1C-46A0-BA1A-C7740940C7A0-low.png"/></fig></li></ul></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-EB89D875-AA2D-47C8-BDC8-58545529CD33" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F548B183-4F51-4D35-BCB0-1EEFCEED1544-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F548B183-4F51-4D35-BCB0-1EEFCEED1544-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Check</b>: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">After positioning of the Aerosol Ink Filter Unit, the free distance in the slit of the hotbox is nominal 4mm. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Check</b>: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The positioning, equal to the unit on the RIGHT-hand side. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-D3746DC6-68B7-4983-B21F-4CEDB64FA5A6" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6E845A23-EC84-4839-9C58-1A691228CB9D-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6E845A23-EC84-4839-9C58-1A691228CB9D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the mirror box. 
</p><note id="GUID-474675FB-8B61-43D9-81FE-3EEA075669C0" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Route the ink hose with the green cable tie below the hot box. 
</p></note><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the 4 screws that are accessible through the 4 holes. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Mount clip. 
